Class NirsitProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • obelab.com.nirsitsdk.NirsitProvider

  • public class NirsitProvider
extends java.lang.Object
     NirsitProvider manages access to a Nirsit device.
 When startMonitoring(), NirsitProvider receive data and invoke callback NirsitProvider.NirsitProviderListener.
